DJ: <i>Good morning.
72 degrees at 6:00.</i>

01:13.950 --> 01:15.751
<i>It is Thursday, August 25th.</i>

01:19.685 --> 01:21.349
<i>This here's what's happening.</i>

01:21.351 --> 01:23.951
<i>A six-alarm fire
burns down seven houses...</i>

01:28.218 --> 01:30.050
<i>Two members
of the US Olympic swim team</i>

01:30.052 --> 01:31.683
<i>being held in Brazil...</i>

01:31.685 --> 01:33.417
